      "date": "2013-07-30 10:00:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n\"It's required to purge caching pages before changing layout, otherwise stale pages would be left in address space which could be read by a process accessing data via mmap interfaces.\"\n\nI though that if layout lock is revoked and layout gen is modified, client will detect it and reconfigure its CLIO, and so, dropping its page cache?",
